/* Parrots!
 * Contains
 * 		Defines
 *		Inventory (headset stuff)
 *		Attack responces
 *		AI
 *		Procs / Verbs (usable by players)
 *		Sub-types
 *		Hear & say (the things we do for gimmicks)
